modName: Amazing Skin for CBBE and Futunarium
summary: Sexy Skin Replacer meshes and textures
descriptionHtml:
Sexy Skin for CBBE with big ass and big tits. And a skin for Futunarium.

- What you need to use :

Caliente's Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE- : http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
For the Futa skin : Futanarium - http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10791/?

- Installation :

Manually copy and paste the Data folder to your Skyrim folder.
It's generally in C:Program Files (x86)/Steam/steamapps/common/skyrim

- Uninstallation :

Just delete any files from this mod.

- Credits :

If want, you can use this in your mod but credit me.
